CatDescriptText: Mrs. Florence Merchant, 2 Horton Street, was part of a man on the street column entitled "Amos 'n' Andy Television Show Offends Some, Pleases Others," published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 28, 1951, pg. 3
